      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">draw</span></div>
        <h3>Brand Content GPT</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Writes in your voice. Trained on your previous copy, your style guide, and your brand rules. Generates emails, social posts, and ads that actually sound like you.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">gavel</span></div>
        <h3>Legal & Compliance GPT</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Built for regulated industries. Answers questions about internal policies, contracts, and compliance procedures — with guardrails that prevent it from giving legal advice it shouldn't.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="icon-box"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#006875; font-size:24px;">hub</span></div>
        <h3>Connected API GPT</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.875rem; line-height:1.7;">Goes beyond documents. Uses GPT Actions to pull live data from your CRM, check order status, create tickets, and update records — all from a chat interface.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="section" style="background:#e7eeff;" aria-labelledby="process-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">How It Works</div>
      <h2 id="process-heading">From Brief to Live GPT</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-connector"></div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-circle">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:22px;">description</span>
        </div>
        <span style="color:#006875; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:4px;">Step 1</span>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:4px;">Brief & Scope</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; line-height:1.6;">We define the GPT's purpose, audience, and what knowledge it needs to do its job.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-circle">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:22px;">upload_file</span>
        </div>
        <span style="color:#006875; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:4px;">Step 2</span>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:4px;">Build & Train</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; line-height:1.6;">We configure the system prompt, upload your knowledge files, set up any API connections, and apply your brand rules.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-circle">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:22px;">science</span>
        </div>
        <span style="color:#006875; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:4px;">Step 3</span>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:4px;">Test & Refine</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; line-height:1.6;">We run it through real scenarios, edge cases, and adversarial questions, then tune until it performs exactly as intended.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-circle">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="color:#00e3fd; font-size:22px;">rocket_launch</span>
        </div>
        <span style="color:#006875; font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em; margin-bottom:4px;">Step 4</span>
        <h3 style="font-weight:700; font-size:0.9375rem; color:#00253b; margin-bottom:4px;">Deploy & Hand Off</h3>
        <p style="color:#42474e; font-size:0.8125rem; line-height:1.6;">We publish it to your team or customers, train your admins on how to update it, and hand over full ownership.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section" style="background:#f9f9ff;" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
